metadata.name: Assembly Required 1
metadata.description:
Gameboy DMG

'Assembly Required' represents a full year of work of careful sourcing, disassembly and arrangement. 

Each piece is comprised of roughly 300 photographs, image-stacked and painstakingly masked together to form an exploded view of these iconic devices

Richard Parry, 2019
4800x6000pix, PNG
1/15
